; Test 'account' as a bare term in query context
; Note: despite TOK_ACCOUNT existing in the token enum, the lexer does NOT
; recognize 'account' as a keyword -- it becomes a plain TERM.
; Here 'account' matches nothing (no account name contains "account"),
; and 'Food' matches via implicit OR, so only Food entries appear.

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $25.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/02 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas    $40.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/03 Restaurant
    Expenses:Food:Dining    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg account Food -> 0
24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $25.00       $25.00
24-Jan-03 Restaurant            Expenses:Food:Dining         $50.00       $75.00
end test
